                Mr. Wedgwood Benn
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-38d90b27-cfa3-4fb5-b2f5-685d88f06ada" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
