<p class="">Would the right hon. Gentleman say that that would be so if the Conference had been in Berlin or Rome?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9a0ecb98-fd02-462f-93d6-9fc788af0899" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
