                Sir H. Croft
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8fbeb0b4-ffa6-4fbc-a659-cda909903ef5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
