        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will not the hon. Gentleman agree that even if it has not limited the duration of the conflict it has limited the size of the conflict?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a7e81c67-c9a8-44e7-a94c-d1bbec9523ae" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
