                Mr. Lennox-Boyd
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b8a9df73-0562-47c0-a050-1053d4311052" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-07-15/debates/03239bf5-bf94-4ee4-b0b3-2b6565964bc4/Spain(Non-InterventionProposals)#contribution-b8a9df73-0562-47c0-a050-1053d4311052">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
