                Colonel Wedgwood
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-eb27857a-7253-4705-8bb1-0f3fed2b05ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-07-15/debates/03239bf5-bf94-4ee4-b0b3-2b6565964bc4/Spain(Non-InterventionProposals)#contribution-eb27857a-7253-4705-8bb1-0f3fed2b05ca">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the hon. Gentleman give the evidence for that statement?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-eb27857a-7253-4705-8bb1-0f3fed2b05ca" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1937-07-15/debates/03239bf5-bf94-4ee4-b0b3-2b6565964bc4/Spain(Non-InterventionProposals)#contribution-eb27857a-7253-4705-8bb1-0f3fed2b05ca">
