        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-810f65c8-17e8-40e0-97e8-746605734f4b'>
            
<p class=""><em>It being Eleven of the Clock, the Motion for the Adjournment lapsed, without Question put.</em></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
